data.description: Welcome Home!  This lovely boasts 4 bedrooms and 2.5 bathrooms on a lot of over an acre!  You have your choice of Primary Suites, one downstairs and one upstairs. Two storage buildings in back yard. One is a huge 10x20 newer building, and the other is a combo storage/lawn equipment/playhouse unit.  Area behind the fence is part of the lot-can be left as is, or cleared. Peaceful area!
